# Sabagiro — Agent Context

**This workspace is Sabagiro only.** Do not implement features in `Fintech Pay` / LariPay unless the user explicitly asks.

## Project

Standalone Next.js 14 club site — tickets, shop, account, admin, door scan.

| | |
|--|--|
| **Path** | `~/Desktop/sabagiro` (repo root) |
| **Production** | https://sabagiro.vercel.app |
| **DB** | PostgreSQL on Railway (`DATABASE_URL`) |
| **Dev** | `npm run dev` → http://localhost:**3001** (not 3000 — LariPay often uses 3000) |

## Key routes

- `/` — homepage (`public/index.html` via `app/route.ts`)
- `/shop`, `/cart`, `/location`
- `/login`, `/register`, `/account`, `/account/settings`
- `/admin/*` — events, users, tickets, generate QR
- `/scan/[token]` — door check; admin can mark USED

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.local.example .env.local   # DATABASE_URL + AUTH_SECRET
npm install
npm run setup:db
npm run dev
```

Test logins: `admin@sabagiro.test` / `SabagiroAdmin2026!`, `user@sabagiro.test` / `SabagiroUser2026!`

## Style

Brutalist dark UI: `#0a0a0a`, acid `#c8ff00`, `globals.css` + `SiteChrome`. Match existing patterns; ka + en copy when user writes in Georgian.

## Pitfalls

- Wrong host: `laripay.vercel.app` has no Sabagiro routes → 404
- Merch: preview only; checkout is tickets only (no payment gateway yet)
- Do not commit `.env.local` or secrets

